info.name: Simple2R2C
info.description: A simple thermal R1C1 model with sinusoidal outside air temperature and a feedback controlled heater.

Ce.port.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ci.port.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Rea.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

Rie.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

preHeat.port.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

prescribedHeatFlow.port.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

senTZone.port.Q_flow.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ai.k.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

preHeat.alpha.comment: Temperature coefficient of heat flow rate

prescribedHeatFlow.alpha.comment: Temperature coefficient of heat flow rate

Ce.port.Q_flow.$pDERA.dummyVarA.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ci.port.Q_flow.$pDERA.dummyVarA.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Rea.Q_flow.$pDERA.dummyVarA.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

Rie.Q_flow.$pDERA.dummyVarA.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

preHeat.port.Q_flow.$pDERA.dummyVarA.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

prescribedHeatFlow.port.Q_flow.$pDERA.du.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ce.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDER.dummyVarFMIDE.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ci.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDER.dummyVarFMIDE.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Rea.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDER.dummyVarFMIDER.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

Rie.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDER.dummyVarFMIDER.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

preHeat.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDER.dummyVar.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

prescribedHeatFlow.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMID.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ce.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarF.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Ci.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarF.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

Rea.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDE.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

Rie.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDE.comment: Heat flow rate from port_a -> port_b

preHeat.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dumm.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

prescribedHeatFlow.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMID.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

senTZone.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dum.comment: Heat flow rate (positive if flowing from outside into the component)

equation: assert(prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref, has value: " + String(prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref, "g"));
assert(preHeat.T_ref >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= preHeat.T_ref, has value: " + String(preHeat.T_ref, "g"));
assert(Ci.T >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= Ci.T, has value: " + String(Ci.T, "g"));
assert(Ce.T >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= Ce.T, has value: " + String(Ce.T, "g"));

(-Ai.y) * (prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref)) - Ai.y.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref))

data: prescribedHeatFlow.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT = (-Ai.y) * (prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref)) - Ai.y.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref))

prescribedHeatFlow.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT = (-Ai.y) * (prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref)) - Ai.y.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref))

(-Ai.y) * (prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref)) - Ai.y.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + prescribedHeatFlow.alpha * (Ci.T - prescribedHeatFlow.T_ref))

equation: (-phi_h) * (preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - preHeat.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + preHeat.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref)) - phi_h.SeedFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref))

data: preHeat.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT = (-phi_h) * (preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - preHeat.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + preHeat.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref)) - phi_h.SeedFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref))

preHeat.port.Q_flow.$pDERFMIDERINIT.dummyVarFMIDERINIT = (-phi_h) * (preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - preHeat.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + preHeat.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref)) - phi_h.SeedFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref))

(-phi_h) * (preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T.SeedFMIDERINIT - preHeat.T_ref.SeedFMIDERINIT) + preHeat.alpha.SeedFMIDERINIT * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref)) - phi_h.SeedFMIDERINIT * (1.0 + preHeat.alpha * (Ci.T - preHeat.T_ref))
